            <fr:title text="Determinants and traces">Determinants and traces</fr:title>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>The last thing to discuss before moving away from matrices: determinants. These give us a way to determine if a matrix is invertible or not.</html:p>
            <html:p>Determinants are related to the trace of a matrix, so we will also discuss them here.</html:p>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="/alex-nelson/" title="Alex Nelson" uri="http://localhost:8000/alex-nelson/" display-uri="alex-nelson" type="local">Alex Nelson</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
                </fr:authors>
                <fr:date>
                  <fr:year>2025</fr:year>
                  <fr:month>7</fr:month>
                  <fr:day>18</fr:day>
                </fr:date>
