              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>The explicit formula for the determinant of a <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[2\times  2]]></fr:tex>-matrix is:</html:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\det \begin {pmatrix}a & b\\c & d\end {pmatrix}=ad-bc]]></fr:tex>
              </fr:mainmatter>
