                <fr:title text="Determinant of matrix with a zero row or zero column is zero">Determinant of matrix with a zero row or zero column is zero</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>lemma</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {A}]]></fr:tex> be an <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n\times  n]]></fr:tex> matrix. If a column of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {A}]]></fr:tex> is all zero (or if a row of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {A}]]></fr:tex> is all zero), then <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\det (\mathbf {A})=0]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
