                <fr:title text="Levi-Civita symbol in three-dimensions">Levi-Civita symbol in three-dimensions</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>example</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>In three dimensions, we have:</html:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\varepsilon _{1,2,3}=\varepsilon _{2,3,1}=\varepsilon _{3,1,2}=+1]]></fr:tex>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\varepsilon _{3,2,1}=\varepsilon _{1,3,2}=\varepsilon _{2,1,3}=-1]]></fr:tex>
                <html:p>And all other entries vanish.</html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
