                <fr:title text="Determinant in terms of Levi-Civita symbols">Determinant in terms of Levi-Civita symbols</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>theorem</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>For a <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[3\times  3]]></fr:tex> matrix <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {A}=(a_{i,j})]]></fr:tex>, we have <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\det (\mathbf {A})=\sum ^{3}_{i=1}\sum ^{3}_{j=1}\sum ^{3}_{k=1}\varepsilon _{i,j,k}a_{1,i}a_{2,j}a_{3,k}]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
                <html:p>For a <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[4\times  4]]></fr:tex> matrix <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {A}=(a_{i,j})]]></fr:tex>, we have <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\det (\mathbf {A})=\sum ^{4}_{i=1}\sum ^{4}_{j=1}\sum ^{4}_{k=1}\sum ^{4}_{\ell =1}\varepsilon _{i,j,k,\ell }a_{1,i}a_{2,j}a_{3,k}a_{4,\ell }]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
                <html:p>For a generic <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[n\times  n]]></fr:tex> matrix <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {A}=(a_{i,j})]]></fr:tex>, we have:</html:p>
                <fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\det (\mathbf {A})=\sum ^{n}_{i_{1}=1}\sum ^{n}_{i_{2}=1}…\sum ^{n}_{i_{n}=1}\varepsilon _{i_{1},i_{2},…,i_{n}}a_{1,i_{1}}a_{2,i_{2}}(\cdots )a_{n,i_{n}}]]></fr:tex>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
